---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const base = '/Jo-Ah-Kim-s-History-Trip';
---

<Layout title="Practicalities" description="Essential travel information for Vietnam, including e-visas, packing guidance, and trip style.">
  <main class="container">
    <header class="page-header">
      <h1 class="page-title">Practicalities</h1>
      <p class="page-subtitle">Essential information for a smooth and respectful journey.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="practical-grid">
      <div class="practical-main">
        <section class="visa-section card">
          <h2 class="section-title">Vietnam E-Visa</h2>
          <p>As of 2026, the official Vietnam E-Visa is required for most visitors. Citizens of Switzerland and Liechtenstein can apply for a **90-day multiple-entry e-visa** directly on the official government portal.</p>
          <p class="accent-note"><em>Warning: Use only the official government domains listed below to avoid third-party agency fees.</em></p>
          <div class="visa-links">
            <a href="https://evisa.gov.vn" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-outline small">Official Portal 1 (evisa.gov.vn)</a>
            <a href="https://thithucdientu.gov.vn" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-outline small">Official Portal 2 (thithucdientu.gov.vn)</a>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="packing-section card mt-lg">
          <h2 class="section-title">What to Pack</h2>
          <div class="packing-grid">
            <div class="pack-item">
              <h3>Climate-Ready</h3>
              <p>Vietnam in May is **hot and humid**. Breathable, light linens and cottons are essential for maximum comfort.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pack-item">
              <h3>Respectful Attire</h3>
              <p>Mausoleums, pagodas, and some imperial sites require shoulders and knees to be covered. A light scarf or dedicated temple outfit is recommended.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pack-item">
              <h3>Comfort First</h3>
              <p>The journey involves moderate walking on historic stones and uneven terrain. Bring well-broken-in, comfortable walking shoes.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>

      <aside class="practical-sidebar">
        <div class="style-card card">
          <h3 class="sidebar-title">Trip Style</h3>
          <p>This is a private, family-oriented historical gift-trip. The pace is curated for a milestone 70th birthday, focusing on depth over breadth.</p>
          <ul class="style-list">
            <li>Private Expert Guides</li>
            <li>Five-Star Historic Stays</li>
            <li>Domestic Regional Flights</li>
            <li>Moderate Walking Activity</li>
            <li>Restrained Group Setting</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="safety-card card mt-md">
          <h3 class="sidebar-title">Useful Links</h3>
          <ul class="link-list">
            <li><a href="https://vietnam.travel/" target="_blank">Vietnam Tourism Official</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://whc.unesco.org/en/list/" target="_blank">UNESCO World Heritage List</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    padding: var(--spacing-lg) 0;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .practical-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .mt-lg {
    margin-top: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .mt-md {
    margin-top: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .visa-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--spacing-sm);
    margin-top: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .accent-note {
    color: #cc0000;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .packing-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--spacing-md);
    margin-top: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .pack-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .sidebar-title {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .style-list, .link-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .style-list li::before {
    content: '•';
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-right: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .link-list li {
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .link-list a {
    text-decoration: underline;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .practical-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
